ghc: ghc (Glasgow Haskell Compilation system)
ghc:
ghc: GHC is a state-of-the-art programming suite for Haskell, a purely
ghc: functional programming language. It includes an optimising compiler
ghc: generating good code for a variety of platforms, together with an
ghc: interactive system for convenient, quick development. The distribution
ghc: includes space and time profiling facilities, a large collection of
ghc: libraries, and support for various language extensions, including
ghc: concurrency, exceptions, and a foreign language interface.
ghc: http://haskell.org/ghc/
